column5: I rear ended a car this morning...I tell you, It is going to be a REALLY bad day!  The driver got out of the other car, and he was a DWARF!!  He looked up at me and said "I am NOT Happy!"  So I said, "Well, then...... which one ARE you?"  That's how the fight started...
I get it...which one are you....bwaaaaa ha ha ha  Good start to the day Roy
Musta hit GRUMPY . . . .     no o o o  o . . . . .      that's you . . . . .    hm m m m  m   m??
lol took me a few but i got it!  Cheers!
LOL, that's a good one Roy!
Ten minutes, ah Chris. Your getting better.
Roy !! you continue to amaze me.
LOL  -  Thanks Roy - I needed that!!!!!   Don
Just may have been the best e-mail I have got this year.Thank GCD and Roy for sharing it here. Joe
